{{Top|leg}}
The '''Kiallquis Mountain Range''' were a group of mountains on the jungle [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]]. They had sheer faces well suited toward sponsored [[Speeder/Legends|speeder]] races. The Kiallquis Mountains were considered ideal for rock climbers and adventurers. [[Tarasin]] used to test criminals by lowering them over precipices in the range, but had discontinued the practice by [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]]. Like other Cularin ranges, Tarasin villages and other life dwelled on the lower ridges, but the higher ridges were devoid of life.

